reviewText: The wife loves this series so I got it for her it's on too early for her so she has all these dog the bounty hunter to watch.
I gave this for a gift for my daughter because she loves watching the Dog and I guess she is enjoying it.

The free dvd it comes with is already included in the megaset so when you get it you will have two of the same dvd. so you think you getting a deal by it coming with a free dvd but what it comes with is a duplicate so if you want to crime is on the run dvds then this is what you should get but if you only want one like most people your better off getting the megaset by itself itll prob be cheaper.
But don't get me wrong I LOVE dog the bounty hunter and the dvds themself are so great and I highly recommend this set. I just wanted people to know about this no so great deal.

Happy as can be when presented to my Grandaughter!!!  Absolutely crazy about Dog!!!
Can't wait for next series to be available!!!
iam a satisfy customer i will order again in the furure its good quality and its worth getting and glad i bought it

The Wild Ride Megaset DVD is great but I was very disappointed when I thought I was getting a different additional dvd for a great price and while I was watching it was the same exact one of dvd of The Wild Ride Megaset disc 6. I thought that it wasn't right.
